Paints-Spray_Paints.name: Asian Paints Spray Paint , White Gloss Finish 200ml
Paints-Spray_Paints.description:
ENAMEL SPRAY PAINT  Paint anything instantly with ezyCR8 Spray Paint by Asian Paints that takes 50% lesser time to dry compared to the conventional brush + enamel system.
DIY HOME DCOR  Add a pop of color to your dcor with this Enamel Spray Paint for metal, canvas, glass, wall, and wood surfaces.
SPRAY PAINT FOR  Cars, Bikes, Metal Gates/Grills
EASY TO USE SPRAY  The spray paint comes in an aerosol spray paint can packing that makes it extremely convenient to use.
HIGH GLOSS FINISH  The DIY spray paint is made to provide smooth & durable finish to your projects with high gloss and better adhesion.
CORRECT USE: Spray from a distance of 25-30 cm. Press spray button firmly with steady even strokes while moving can rapidly back and forth. Finger must not protrude over front edge of spray button.
PAINT COVERAGE: The spray paint offers a coverage of 8 to 10 sqft. for 200ml can and 16 to 20 sqft. for 400ml can.

Paints-Acrylics.name: Pidilite Fevicryl Acrylic Colours Sunflower Kit (10 Colors x 15 ml) DIY Paint, Rich Pigment, Non-Craking Paint for Canvas, Wood, Leather, Earthenware, Metal
Paints-Acrylics.description:
Vibrant Colours - Make paintings pop out using the 10 vibrant shades. The Sunflower Acrylic Kit has acrylic colours for creating art and tones that bring out the artistic mood. It lets artists give depth and dimension to their creations
Multisurface Use - The Fevicryl Acrylic Sunflower Kit comprises of vibrant painting colours and refined shades that work across a wide variety of mediums. Apply these paints to various surfaces like wood, canvas, leather, terracotta and even fabrics.
Non-Toxic and Safe -The colouring kit is safe for use by young artists. The paints are made using non-toxic substances and pose no health risk. The cleanup is also very easy after you're done creating art projects.
Very Beginner-Friendly - No need to be an expert artist to use this. Grab a piece of cloth or paper, set up your colouring palette and get ready to have a fun time.

Painting_Medium-Acrylic_Auxilaries.name: Pebeo Studio Acrylic Auxiliaries - Set of 5 Mediums in 40 ML Jars
Painting_Medium-Acrylic_Auxilaries.description:
Set of 5 Mediums in 40 ML Jars; Included - Studio Gloss Bindex, Black Studio Gesso, Studio Modelling Paste, White Sand Texture Gel & Colourless Green Phosphorescent Gel
Black Gesso - To prepare the painting surface use Gesso, this underlay will waterproof, prime and give the desired roughness (for better adhesion of the colour) to the absorbent surface: canvas, paper or wood. An Intense black matt coating, particularly suitable for the application of the DYNA, Studio Acrylics etc.
Gels & Bindex can be mixed with the colours to provide an even colour consistency, to allow better adhesion, transparency, depth, drying time without thinning the paint; Gloss Bindex - Non-yellowing liquid binder for the preparation of the colours. Bindex gives both depth and brightness and is ideal for collages and inlays
Colourless Green Phosphorescent Gel - Of thicker consistency then Bindex, this gel prepares and gives depth to colours but also works to give a touch of phosphorescence to the piece. Phosphorescent gels absorb natural or artificial light and re-emit it in the dark, to glow in the dark
White Sand Texture Gel - This gel contains sand that produces textured and unique dimension effects. It is possible to mix with acrylic colours and mediums, or use them alone; Modeling Paste - Used to create structure and thick textures. It is are very thick, heavy textured, opaque white and renders a matt finish after application. Recommended to use a painting knife to apply it. It is possible to mix it with acrylic colours, but this will result in a colour variation

Painting_Medium-Gessos_and_Grounds.name: Amsterdam Grounds - Gesso - Transparent - 250ml' - Amsterdam Auxiliaries & Drawing Ink - Gesso Transparent - 250 ml
Painting_Medium-Gessos_and_Grounds.description:
Jar of 250 ml provides good adhesion for acrylic paint, oil paint and gouache, etc.
Suitable for absorbent grounds that are free of dust and grease, such as artists canvas (linen, cotton, etc.), wood, plywood, hardboard, cardboard and paper
Suitable as preparation for murals on (alkaline) grounds such as fresh concrete, stucco and bricks
Very absorbent grounds must first be pre-sized with Amsterdam acrylic binder
Can be coloured with acrylic paint Thinnable with water & Waterproof when dry Use at temperatures above 10 C and Store frost-free, cleans utensils with water

Painting_Medium-Fixative_and_Varnishes.name: Brustro Artists Picture Varnish - Satin - 200 ml Spray can
Painting_Medium-Fixative_and_Varnishes.description:
Its Ideal for protection of acrylics , oil , watercolor, etc
Slow drying, non-yellowing varnish
Final picture varnish . Dries to a Satin finish . Waterproof . Made in Spain

Painting_Medium-Oil_Mediums.name: Winsor & Newton Oil Colour Medium Liquin Impasto - 60ml
Painting_Medium-Oil_Mediums.description:
A quick drying, semi-gloss medium which thickens slowly and extends tube colour retaining crisp textures and brush marks without any visible leveling; Speeds drying (touch dry in 1-6 days depending on colour and film thickness)
Resists yellowing, it can become touch dry within one to six days, depending on the colour and film thickness
Not suitable as a varnish or final coat
It has a semi-gloss appearance and can also be used to thicken and extend tube colour whilst retaining crisp textures and brush marks without any visible leveling
Imported
Country of Origin: France

Canvas-Canvas_Rolls.name: Pidilite Fevicryl Fine Art Canvas Roll for Painting, 100% Cotton Canvas Roll, Ideal for Acrylic & Oil Painting, 48" (5m)
Canvas-Canvas_Rolls.description:
VERSATILE CANVAS ROLLS - Fevicryl Fine Art Canvas rolls are Ideal for use with acrylic as well as oil colours. Canvas rolls can we cut into desired shapes or sizes and framed
100% COTTON - This Fevicryl Fine Art canvas roll is crafted from 100% pure cotton. Students prefer it for large paintings, and it supports professional-grade paints on the surface well.
ZERO PERCOLATION - Never worry about paints leaking from the back of these Fevicryl Fine Art canvas rolls. The rolls has a double acrylic titanium priming that prevents any seepages from occurring on the rear side.
IDEAL FOR BEGINNERS & ARTISTS - This canvas rolls are ideal for beginners and artists
SAFE PACKAGING - Fevicryl Fine Art Canvas roll is wrapped in cardboard tube with sturdy box packing to prevent damage.

Canvas-Stretched_Canvas.name: Pidilite Fevicryl Fine Art Stretched Canvas Back Fold for Painting, 100% Cotton Fine Grain Stretched Canvas, Ideal for Acrylic & Oil Painting, (12 X 16 Inch)
Canvas-Stretched_Canvas.description:
STURDY STRETCHED CANVAS - Fevicryl Fine Art stretched canvas is sturdy and long-lasting acrylic and oil canvas stretched canvas for painting, mixed media drawings, and sketching. Unleash your imagination and let your ideas go wild with these. These provide enough space for your creative juices to get flowing.
100% COTTON CANVAS - This Fevicryl Fine Art stretched canvas board is crafted from 100% pure cotton. Cotton stretched canvas boards last a long time, are stretchable and very flexible as a painting medium for artists. Students prefer it for large paintings, and it supports professional-grade paints on the surface well.
ZERO PERCOLATION - Never worry about paints leaking from the back of these Fevicryl Fine Art stretched canvas boards. The canvas has a double acrylic titanium priming that prevents any seepages from occurring on the rear side.
IDEAL FOR BEGINNERS & ARTISTS - This Fevicryl Fine Art stretched canvas board is ideal for beginners and artists. The texture is fine-grain and the boards are suitable for creating fluid artworks. Texture painting and oil painting are supported as well.
